  "text": "In this paper, only the records from the MPA are considered. Indeed, the MPA dimensions correspond to wavelengths ranging from infrasounds to low audible contents (see Table 3 ), it is well adapted to cover the selected 1 Hz-40 Hz frequency band. The MBA dimensions turn out to be too large to correctly detect coherent wavefronts of the considered frequency contents. This statement is in agreement with the results established by [CITATION_1] . Thus, thunder signatures recorded with the MBA are not explored in this paper.",
